{"tid":977703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好彩當年政改無袋住先","createTime":"2019-01-11T11:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T05:54:36.000Z","uid":195944,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0b81b1fb911ed4043599e307e4b58e0bb5a05c61","tid":977703,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:20:41.000Z","msg":"如果過咗 啲冚家鏟就會話當年大部分議員都贊同個政改 唔會再改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就好似依家條富貴話好驚訝當年好多保皇狗贊成依家反對65歲攞綜援個政策<br />\n<br />\n一句共狗講嘅野 一定唔好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一蟈兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90df370d81112a61ff08b65e4845f83de10fa6a0","tid":977703,"uid":30578,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"夾鳩埋做戲咋"},{"pid":"6fce547977d71959c882401ec74d012bec1ab47e","tid":977703,"uid":195944,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"啲疑似民主黨同人講政治道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地有無諗過對手係班專偷呃拐騙搶嘅土匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有隻小學都未畢業嘅雜種狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對住啲咁嘅生物仲要講誠信？high撚大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06ca8f03317a8ea2e608594def5cc5a4fb38974","tid":977703,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:34:49.000Z","msg":"如果用個政改選咗個特首出黎仲衰<br />\n<br />\n到時就會同全世界講係全港人選出黎 狆蟈有民主 一蟈兩制好成功 台灣咁做都無問題 <br />\n<br />\n仆街啦 共匪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6777a51d11adfb328f6d57fcd71280e49d8b5f","tid":977703,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9941ea1831500b1a9488621025adf2a967e1c9ed","tid":977703,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:07:52.000Z","msg":"容海恩發問時表示，很多市民對長者綜援申請年齡提升「大感不滿」，並引述特首早前以自己為例說60歲以上仍有工作能力，容海恩認為很難將一般的綜援長者與特首比較，問特首會否收回申請年齡提高的安排。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥重申，申請年齡提升至65歲，並非說65歲以下人士不能申領綜援，60至64歲人士仍可以非長者健全人士身分申領。她又說，近年長者就業率上升，長者投入勞動市場是不爭事實，政府亦有自力更生支援，幫助他們就業。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">林太續說，提升申領年齡是經「各位批准」，並稱今早翻查紀錄，當年提交給立法會的《2018年撥款條例草案》中，社會福利署總目提到在2018至2019年內將長者綜援申領年齡提升至65歲，她又指，對議員如今反對這項安排感到「很驚訝」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話ok喎 依家又唔俾 即係點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1497db70b435874010f3e90b7b91e06798b4911","tid":977703,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:36:03.000Z","msg":"毒撚開po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a364fae6c109dececd6175b6ffdcabf0ab924d","tid":977703,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T15:16:09.000Z","msg":"袋咗咪有曾俊華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c6f40b8ab2412d1551d9ff47a2d1c999968949","tid":977703,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T15:17:00.000Z","msg":"而家差唔多姐 話你地自己放棄咪撚再求我"},{"pid